Softwares Used:

1. Apache tomcat 9.0.14
2. java 8
3. Spring 5.2.3 - Uses Spring security
4. No DataBase Integration


Urls to Run:

   http://localhost:8080/login-demo-app/antiquedata/login
   
   or 
   
   http://localhost:8080/login-demo-app/antiquedata/
   
   
   
Roles: ADMIN and USER



Credentials: 
  
    admin/admin
    
    user/user
   
